e rising river."},{"name":"Elrond","aliases":["Peredhil","Half-Elf"],"importance":"secondary","status":"unknown","lastSeen":"Helm's Deep","currentLocation":"Unknown (departed to the West)","description":"The half-Elf ruler of Rivendell known for his wisdom and his connection to the Valar.","relationships":[{"character":"Galadriel","relationship":"Spouse"},{"character":"Celebrían","relationship":"Wife (not a direct quote but her spouse)"}],"recentEvents":"Departed for the West aboard the ship."},{"name":"Legolas Greenleaf","aliases":["Legolas","Elladan","Elrohir"],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"The Dawn","currentLocation":"Minas Tirith","description":"Half-elven son of Elrond, aiding Aragorn in his quest against Sauron","relationships":[{"character":"Aragorn","relationship":"Allies with"}],"recentEvents":"Supported Gandalf's strategic counsel against Sauron."},{"name":"Gimli","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"The Tower of the Stone of Erech","currentLocation":"Minas Tirith","description":"Dwarf from the Lonely Mountain, loyal and brave.","relationships":[{"character":"Aragorn","relationship":"friend"},{"character":"Legolas","relationship":"friend"}],"recentEvents":"Fought alongside Legolas, wielding his axe with valor."},{"name":"Balin","aliases":[],"importance":"minor","status":"dead","lastSeen":"The Bridge of Khazad-dûm","currentLocation":"The Chamber of Mazarbul in Moria","description":"Formerly a member of the Fellowship but died previously in Moria.","relationships":[{"character":"Gimli","relationship":"Descendant, looks for his kin's tomb"},{"character":"Gandalf","relationship":"Former companion"}],"recentEvents":"His tomb was discovered inside Moria."},{"name":"The Balrog","aliases":["Durin's Bane"],"importance":"villain","status":"unknown","lastSeen":"The Bridge of Khazad-dûm","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"A shadowy creature of immense power.","relationships":[{"character":"Gandalf","relationship":"Foe"},{"character":"Aragorn","relationship":"Foe"},{"character":"Boromir","relationship":"Foe"},{"character":"Legolas","relationship":"Foe"},{"character":"Gimli","relationship":"Foe"},{"character":"Frodo","relationship":"Foe"},{"character":"Sam","relationship":"Foe"},{"character":"Merry and Pippin","relationship":"Foe"}],"recentEvents":"Engaged in a deadly battle with Gandalf."},{"name":"Haldir","aliases":[],"importance":"minor","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Fëanorian Art","currentLocation":"Lothlórien","description":"An Elf warrior and guide who leads the travelers within Lothlórien.","relationships":[{"character":"Galadriel","relationship":"Works for and respects the Lady of Lothlórien"},{"character":"Frodo","relationship":"Guide and caretaker"}],"recentEvents":"Guides Frodo and Sam to Cerin Amroth and describes the power of the land to them."},{"name":"Lady Galadriel","aliases":["Elven-lady","Guardian of Lórien"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 6 - Lothlórien","currentLocation":"Lothlórien","description":"An Elven queen of immense power and wisdom, keeper of the Ring Nenya.","relationships":[{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"met and tested"},{"character":"Samwise Gamgee","relationship":"met"}],"recentEvents":"Galadriel tested Frodo's resolve and offered to take the One Ring, but refused it in favor of continuing her duties to Middle-earth."},{"name":"Galadriel","aliases":["Lady of Lothlórien"],"importance":"secondary","status":"unknown","lastSeen":"Fangorn","currentLocation":"Unknown (departed to the West)","description":"A queen of the elven realm of Lothlórien, she possessed the Light of Eärendil and the Mirror of Galadriel.","relationships":[{"character":"Elrond","relationship":"Spouse"},{"character":"Celeborn","relationship":"Husband (not a direct quote but her consort)"}],"recentEvents":"Departed for the West aboard the ship."},{"name":"Saruman","aliases":["The White Wizard","Curunir","Sharkey","Curumo"],"importance":"main","status":"dead","lastSeen":"Bag End","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"A corrupted former Maia who became the chief opponent to the Fellowship and sought the power of the One Ring.","relationships":[{"character":"Sauron","relationship":"Servant and collaborator"}],"recentEvents":"Attacked Frodo but survived, killed by Wormtongue, then vanished."},{"name":"Treebeard","aliases":["Fangorn"],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"The White Rider","currentLocation":"Fangorn's Wood","description":"A very old and wise Ent, Treebeard is the master of the forest.","relationships":[{"character":"Gandalf","relationship":"Acquaintance"},{"character":"Merry","relationship":"Friend"},{"character":"Pippin","relationship":"Friend"}],"recentEvents":"Treebeard agreed to keep an eye on Saruman trapped in Orthanc."},{"name":"Bregalad","aliases":["Quickbeam"],"importance":"minor","status":"alive","lastSeen":"The Ent's Fangs","currentLocation":"Valley of Saruman","description":"A young Ent who was part of the march of the Ents.","relationships":[{"character":"Treebeard","relationship":"Fellow Ent"}],"recentEvents":"Joined the march as one of the Ents going to Isengard."},{"name":"Éomer son of Éomund","aliases":["King of Rohan","Lord of the Mark","Théoden","Théoden King"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"The Palantír","currentLocation":"Minas Tirith","description":"King of Rohan, a powerful warrior and leader.","relationships":[{"character":"Aragorn","relationship":"ally"},{"character":"Imrahil","relationship":"ally"}],"recentEvents":"Fought valiantly alongside Aragorn, uniting the forces of Rohan and Gondor to defeat Mordor's armies."},{"name":"Erkenbrand","aliases":["Erkenbrand Lord of Westfold"],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Unknown","currentLocation":"Helm's Gate","description":"Lord of Westfold, a warrior and leader of a great part of Rohan's forces. He arrived with reinforcements after the Horn of Helm was blown.","relationships":[{"character":"Théoden","relationship":"allies and fellow warriors"},{"character":"Éomer","relationship":"commander of an army"}],"recentEvents":"Arrived with a thousand men to reinforce Théoden's forces."},{"name":"Wormtongue","aliases":["Gríma","The spy"],"importance":"secondary","status":"dead","lastSeen":"Bag End","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"Saruman's servant and enforcer, who aided Saruman in his downfall by betraying Rohan and the Shire.","relationships":[{"character":"Saruman","relationship":"Servant and minion"}],"recentEvents":"Killed Saruman out of hatred and fear."},{"name":"Sméagol","aliases":["Sméagol","Gollum","Slinker","Stinker"],"importance":"minor","status":"dead","lastSeen":"The Passage of the Marshes","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"A treacherous hobbit who was obsessed with the One Ring and ultimately led Frodo to Mount Doom.","relationships":[{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Accompanied and conflicted over the Ring"},{"character":"Samwise Gamgee","relationship":"Foe and competitor for the Ring"}],"recentEvents":"Gollum falls to his death into a fiery abyss, resulting in the destruction of the One Ring."},{"name":"Gollum/Sméagol","aliases":["the creeping Sméagol"],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"The Window on the World","currentLocation":"Ithilien","description":"A creature of ambiguous moral standing, formerly known as Sméagol, who guides Frodo with a mix of malevolent intention and dependency on the Ring.","relationships":[{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Guide and reluctant companion"},{"character":"Faramir","relationship":"Detected by Faramir as having committed murder and possessing malice"}],"recentEvents":"Guides Frodo across dangerous and ominous Ithilien; warned against cirith Ungol by Faramir."},{"name":"Shelob","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"A Prisoner in Barad-dûr","currentLocation":"Tunnel complex under Bara