al but tempted by the Ring.","relationships":[{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Member of the Fellowship"},{"character":"Aragorn","relationship":"Trusted member of the Fellowship"}],"recentEvents":"Bowed his head and showed respect as they passed through the Argonath."},{"name":"Legolas","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Many Meetings","currentLocation":"Anduin River","description":"An Elven prince and member of the Fellowship, providing valuable tracking abilities and archery.","relationships":[{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Travel companion and friend"},{"character":"Aragorn","relationship":"Travel companion and friend"},{"character":"Gimli","relationship":"Travel companion and friend"}],"recentEvents":"Departs from Lórien with the remainder of the Fellowship. Comforts Gimli about the farewell to Galadriel."},{"name":"Gimli","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Farewell to Lórien","currentLocation":"Anduin River","description":"A dwarf and a member of the Fellowship, who is emotionally affected by the departure from Galadriel.","relationships":[{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Travel companion and friend"},{"character":"Aragorn","relationship":"Travel companion and friend"},{"character":"Legolas","relationship":"Travel companion and friend"}],"recentEvents":"Departs from Lórien with the remainder of the Fellowship. Steers the boats down the River Anduin."},{"name":"Balin","aliases":[],"importance":"minor","status":"dead","lastSeen":"The Bridge of Khazad-dûm","currentLocation":"The Chamber of Mazarbul in Moria","description":"Formerly a member of the Fellowship but died previously in Moria.","relationships":[{"character":"Gimli","relationship":"Descendant, looks for his kin's tomb"},{"character":"Gandalf","relationship":"Former companion"}],"recentEvents":"His tomb was discovered inside Moria."},{"name":"The Balrog","aliases":["Durin's Bane"],"importance":"villain","