oodland Realm who became part of the Fellowship of the Ring","relationships":[{"character":"Thranduil","relationship":"father"},{"character":"Gandalf","relationship":"friend and ally"}],"recentEvents":"Legolas, with Aragorn and Gimli, set out on foot after their horses disappeared in Fangorn Forest. They encounter the forest's eerie qualities and the disappearance of their horses."},{"name":"Gimli","aliases":["son of Glóin"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Lothlórien","currentLocation":"Fangorn Forest","description":"A Dwarf who became part of the Fellowship of the Ring","relationships":[{"character":"Gandalf","relationship":"ally"},{"character":"Thorin Oakenshield","relationship":"ancestor"}],"recentEvents":"Gimli, with Aragorn and Legolas, set out on foot after the horses they had borrowed from Rohan were taken or scared away by a mysterious old man, possibly Saruman. The companions are now wary and cautious in the mysterious forest of Fangorn."},{"name":"Balin","aliases":[],"importance":"minor","status":"dead","lastSeen":"The Bridge of Khazad-dûm","currentLocation":"The Chamber of Mazarbul in Moria","description":"Formerly a member of the Fellowship but died previously in Moria.","relationships":[{"character":"Gimli","relationship":"Descendant, looks for his kin's tomb"},{"character":"Gandalf","relationship":"Former companion"}],"recentEvents":"His tomb was discovered inside Moria."},{"name":"The Balrog","aliases":["Durin's Bane"],"importance":"villain","status":"unknown","lastSeen":"The Bridge of Khazad-dûm","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"A shadowy creature of immense power.","relationships":[{"character":"Gandalf","relationship":"Foe"},{"character":"Aragorn","relationship":"Foe"},{"character":"Boromir","relationship":"Foe"},{"character":"Legolas","relationship":"Foe"},{"character":"Gimli","relationship":"Foe"},{"character":"Frodo","relationship":"Foe"},{"character":"Sam","relationship":"Foe"},{"character":"Merry and Pippin","relatio