ions with a song, assists Tom in welcoming them to their house."},{"name":"Strider","aliases":["Aragorn","Strider","Estel","Elessar"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"The Breaking of the Fellowship","currentLocation":"Eastemnet, Rohan","description":"A Ranger of the North and heir to the thrones of Gondor and Arnor, traveling with the Fellowship.","relationships":[{"character":"Gandalf","relationship":"Allies"},{"character":"Legolas","relationship":"Allies"},{"character":"Gimli","relationship":"Allies"}],"recentEvents":"Joined Gandalf and the others in riding to Théoden’s aid, having received guidance from the wizard."},{"name":"Barliman Butterbur","aliases":["The innkeeper"],"importance":"minor","status":"alive","lastSeen":"The Shadow of the Past","currentLocation":"The Prancing Pony","description":"Innkeeper who helps Frodo and his companions but is cautious due to their strange behavior","relationships":[{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Host (hostility developing)"},{"character":"Strider","relationship":"Guest (knowledge of each other's true roles under question)"}],"recentEvents":"Handles the upset caused by Frodo's use of the Ring, tries to understand the situation"},{"name":"Mugwort","aliases":[],"importance":"minor","status":"alive","lastSeen":"The Great River","currentLocation":"The Prancing Pony","description":"Local Hobbit who witnessed Frodo’s vanishing act","relationships":[{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Witness"}],"recentEvents":"Reports to Barliman Butterbur about Frodo's disappearance"},{"name":"Nob","aliases":[],"importance":"minor","status":"alive","lastSeen":"The Fellowship of the Ring: The Black Riders","currentLocation":"Bree","description":"A servant at the inn tasked by Mr. Butterbur to help Hobbits.","relationships":[{"character":"Strider","relationship":"Employer or Guide"},{"character":"Mr. Butterbur","relationship":"Employer"}],"recentEvents":"Located the hobbits, helped arrange their bedding and he