 of Elrond and supports Frodo's decision to accept the burden of the One Ring."},{"name":"Boromir","aliases":["Captain of Gondor"],"importance":"main","status":"dead","lastSeen":"Farewell to Lórien","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"A captain of Gondor, member of the Fellowship of the Ring.","relationships":[{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Fellow traveler and protector"}],"recentEvents":"Left the others after the boats incident to follow the two hobbits."},{"name":"Legolas","aliases":[],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"The Breaking of the Fellowship","currentLocation":"Eastemnet, Rohan","description":"An Elf from Mirkwood with keen eyesight and a keen sense of history, part of the Fellowship of the Ring.","relationships":[{"character":"Aragorn","relationship":"Allies"},{"character":"Gimli","relationship":"Allies"}],"recentEvents":"Joined Aragorn and Gimli in riding with Gandalf to Théoden's aid, seeing signs of battle as they traveled."},{"name":"Gimli","aliases":[],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"The Breaking of the Fellowship","currentLocation":"Eastemnet, Rohan","description":"A Dwarf from Erebor with a love for good beer and battle, part of the Fellowship of the Ring.","relationships":[{"character":"Aragorn","relationship":"Allies"},{"character":"Legolas","relationship":"Allies"}],"recentEvents":"Joined Gandalf and his friends in riding to Théoden’s aid, expressing eagerness to see war and battle."},{"name":"Balin","aliases":[],"importance":"minor","status":"dead","lastSeen":"The Bridge of Khazad-dûm","currentLocation":"The Chamber of Mazarbul in Moria","description":"Formerly a member of the Fellowship but died previously in Moria.","relationships":[{"character":"Gimli","relationship":"Descendant, looks for his kin's tomb"},{"character":"Gandalf","relationship":"Former companion"}],"recentEvents":"His tomb was discovered inside Moria."},{"name":"The Balrog","aliases":["Durin's Bane"],"importance":"villain",