iption":"Heir to the throne of Gondor, and a formidable warrior aiding Rohan and Middle-earth.","relationships":[{"character":"Théoden","relationship":"ally, friend"},{"character":"Arwen","relationship":"lover"},{"character":"Legolas","relationship":"travel companion and friend"}],"recentEvents":"Stood with Théoden and fought valiantly against Orcs."},{"name":"Barliman Butterbur","aliases":["The innkeeper"],"importance":"minor","status":"alive","lastSeen":"The Shadow of the Past","currentLocation":"The Prancing Pony","description":"Innkeeper who helps Frodo and his companions but is cautious due to their strange behavior","relationships":[{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Host (hostility developing)"},{"character":"Strider","relationship":"Guest (knowledge of each other's true roles under question)"}],"recentEvents":"Handles the upset caused by Frodo's use of the Ring, tries to understand the situation"},{"name":"Mugwort","aliases":[],"importance":"minor","status":"alive","lastSeen":"The Great River","currentLocation":"The Prancing Pony","description":"Local Hobbit who witnessed Frodo’s vanishing act","relationships":[{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Witness"}],"recentEvents":"Reports to Barliman Butterbur about Frodo's disappearance"},{"name":"Nob","aliases":[],"importance":"minor","status":"alive","lastSeen":"The Fellowship of the Ring: The Black Riders","currentLocation":"Bree","description":"A servant at the inn tasked by Mr. Butterbur to help Hobbits.","relationships":[{"character":"Strider","relationship":"Employer or Guide"},{"character":"Mr. Butterbur","relationship":"Employer"}],"recentEvents":"Located the hobbits, helped arrange their bedding and head imitations, and assisted in the watch on the doors."},{"name":"Mister Butterbur","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"The Prancing Pony","currentLocation":"Bree","description":"The innkeeper of The Prancing Pony, who helps Frodo and company with local information and lodging.","relationships":[{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Accommodations and Information Provider"},{"character":"Meriadoc Brandybuck","relationship":"Guest"},{"character":"Peregrin Took","relationship":"Guest"}],"recentEvents":"Sent Nob to help the hobbits and watch for any disturbances around the inn."},{"name":"Glorfindel","aliases":["Elf-lord"],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Flight to the Ford","currentLocation":"Ford of Bruinen","description":"An Elf-lord who helps protect Frodo from the Black Riders.","relationships":[{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Helper and guide"}],"recentEvents":"Glorfindel rode ahead of Frodo on his white horse Asfaloth to ward off the Black Riders and protect Frodo from capture."},{"name":"Black Riders","aliases":["Ringwraiths","Nazgul"],"importance":"secondary","status":"dead","lastSeen":"Flight to the Ford","currentLocation":"Ford of Bruinen","description":"Nine dark figures on black horses, they are servants of Sauron seeking the One Ring.","relationships":[{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Pursuers"},{"character":"Sauron","relationship":"Servant"}],"recentEvents":"Nine Black Riders attempted to capture Frodo at the Ford of Bruinen, but were repelled by Glorfindel and overcome by the rising river."},{"name":"Elrond","aliases":["Lord Elrond"],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Inn at Bree","currentLocation":"Rivendell","description":"Elven lord and keeper of the Three Elven Rings of Power.","relationships":[{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Council leader"},{"character":"Gandalf","relationship":"Friend and ally"}],"recentEvents":"Presents the Council of Elrond and supports Frodo's decision to accept the burden of the One Ring."},{"name":"Boromir","aliases":["Captain of Gondor"],"importance":"main","status":"dead","lastSeen":"Farewell to Lórien","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"A captain of Gondor, member of the Fellowship of the Ring.","relationships":[{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Fellow traveler and protector"}],"recentEvents":"Left the others after the boats incident to follow the two hobbits."},{"name":"Legolas","aliases":[],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"The Breaking of the Fellowship","currentLocation":"Eastemnet, Rohan","description":"An Elf from Mirkwood with keen eyesight and a keen sense of history, part of the Fellowship of the Ring.","relationships":[{"character":"Aragorn","relationship":"Allies"},{"character":"Gimli","relationship":"Allies"}],"recentEvents":"Joined Aragorn and Gimli in riding with Gandalf to Théoden's aid, seeing signs of battle as they traveled."},{"name":"Gimli","aliases":[],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"The Breaking of the Fellowship","currentLocation":"Eastemnet, Rohan","description":"A Dwarf from Erebor with a love for good beer and battle, part of the Fellowship of the Ring.","relationships":[{"character":"Aragorn","relationship":"Allies"},{"character":"Legolas","relationship":"Allies"}],"recentEvents":"Joined Gandalf and his friends in riding to Théoden’s aid, expressing eagerness to see war and battle."},{"name":"Balin","aliases":[],"importance":"minor","status":"dead","lastSeen":"The Bridge of Khazad-dûm","currentLocation":"The Chamber of Mazarbul in Moria","description":"Formerly a member of the Fellowship but died previously in Moria.","relationships":[{"character":"Gimli","relationship":"Descendant, looks for his kin's tomb"},{"character":"Gandalf","relationship":"Former companion"}],"recentEvents":"His tomb was discovered inside Moria."},{"name":"The Balrog","aliases":["Durin's Bane"],"importance":"villain","status":"unknown","lastSeen":"The Bridge of Khazad-dûm","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"A shadowy creature of immense power.","relationships":[{"character":"Gandalf","relationship":"Foe"},{"character":"Aragorn","relationship":"Foe"},{"character":"Boromir","relationship":"Foe"},