e inn."},{"name":"Glorfindel","aliases":["Elf-lord"],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Flight to the Ford","currentLocation":"Ford of Bruinen","description":"An Elf-lord who helps protect Frodo from the Black Riders.","relationships":[{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Helper and guide"}],"recentEvents":"Glorfindel rode ahead of Frodo on his white horse Asfaloth to ward off the Black Riders and protect Frodo from capture."},{"name":"Black Riders","aliases":["Ringwraiths","Nazgul"],"importance":"secondary","status":"dead","lastSeen":"Flight to the Ford","currentLocation":"Ford of Bruinen","description":"Nine dark figures on black horses, they are servants of Sauron seeking the One Ring.","relationships":[{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Pursuers"},{"character":"Sauron","relationship":"Servant"}],"recentEvents":"Nine Black Riders attempted to capture Frodo at the Ford of Bruinen, but were repelled by Glorfindel and overcome by the rising river."},{"name":"Elrond","aliases":["Lord Elrond"],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Inn at Bree","currentLocation":"Rivendell","description":"Elven lord and keeper of the Three Elven Rings of Power.","relationships":[{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Council leader"},{"character":"Gandalf","relationship":"Friend and ally"}],"recentEvents":"Presents the Council of Elrond and supports Frodo's decision to accept the burden of the One Ring."},{"name":"Boromir","aliases":["Captain of Gondor"],"importance":"main","status":"dead","lastSeen":"Farewell to Lórien","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"A captain of Gondor, member of the Fellowship of the Ring.","relationships":[{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Fellow traveler and protector"}],"recentEvents":"Left the others after the boats incident to follow the two hobbits."},{"name":"Legolas Greenleaf","aliases":["Legolas"],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"The Riders of Rohan","curr