imli","relationship":"Met in Lórien, gave him a Lórien brooch"},{"character":"Legolas","relationship":"Met in Lórien, gave him Galadriel's gift of Lórien apples"}],"recentEvents":"Sees the Fellowship off as they leave Lórien."},{"name":"Saruman","aliases":["The White Wizard"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"The Departure of Boromir","currentLocation":"Orthanc","description":"An Istari, now corrupted and plotting against Middle-earth.","relationships":[{"character":"Gandalf","relationship":"Former ally, now enemy"}],"recentEvents":"Saruman refused to leave Orthanc and will be monitored by Ents."},{"name":"Treebeard","aliases":["Fangorn"],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"The White Rider","currentLocation":"Fangorn's Wood","description":"A very old and wise Ent, Treebeard is the master of the forest.","relationships":[{"character":"Gandalf","relationship":"Acquaintance"},{"character":"Merry","relationship":"Friend"},{"character":"Pippin","relationship":"Friend"}],"recentEvents":"Treebeard agreed to keep an eye on Saruman trapped in Orthanc."},{"name":"Bregalad","aliases":["Quickbeam"],"importance":"minor","status":"alive","lastSeen":"The Ent's Fangs","currentLocation":"Valley of Saruman","description":"A young Ent who was part of the march of the Ents.","relationships":[{"character":"Treebeard","relationship":"Fellow Ent"}],"recentEvents":"Joined the march as one of the Ents going to Isengard."},{"name":"Théoden King","aliases":["Théoden","Théoden King","King of the Mark","King Théoden"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Lothlórien","currentLocation":"Isengard","description":"King of Rohan, wise and respected leader.","relationships":[{"character":"Aragorn","relationship":"Allies"},{"character":"Gimli","relationship":"Friend"}],"recentEvents":"Met and greeted Merry and Pippin, expressed curiosity about hobbits."},{"name":"Erkenbrand","aliases":["Erkenbrand Lord of Westfold"],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive",